Basic level emailing program to send emails or texts

Sender email must have:
'Allow third party app access'

To send texts to recepient:
Must have service provider:

AT&T	number@txt.att.net
Sprint	number@pm.sprint.com  or number@messaging.sprintpcs.com
T-Mobile	number@tmomail.net
Verizon Wireless	number@vtext.com
Virgin Mobile	number@vmobl.com
Boost Mobile	number@sms.myboostmobile.com
